 "remarks": "Welcome to 6 Jersey Lane, a beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2 full bathroom home located on a quiet street in desirable East Norwalk. Move-in ready and filled with natural light, this inviting home features gleaming hardwood floors, an open-concept living and dining area, recessed lighting, and a renovated kitchen with white cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample prep space. The spacious living room offers a cozy fireplace and oversized windows, while the generously sized bedrooms and updated bathrooms provide comfort and flexibility for everyday living. Additional space offers the perfect setup for a home office, playroom, or guest accommodations. Outside, enjoy a large level backyard and patio ideal for entertaining, outdoor dining, or relaxing summer evenings, all surrounded by mature landscaping and excellent curb appeal. Conveniently located just minutes from Metro North, beaches, parks, restaurants, shopping, and major highways, this East Norwalk home combines neighborhood charm with exceptional commuter convenience. Sale is contingent upon sellers finding suitable housing",
